	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/ff52dfa21bbe.jpg" width="1080" height="720" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Factory candleholder by Skultuna
</h3>
<p>
	这是一个黄铜制作的烛台，来自瑞典皇室品牌 Skultuna。烛台的形状源于 Skultuna 有着 408 岁的铸造厂，经历过多次大火摧毁和重建，有着特别的纪念意义。烛台的底座是方形的，四面的形状并不相同，表面的镂空窗户让它显得精致而有层次感。有 8.5 厘米高，可经水洗，售价 69 欧元，<a href="http://www.finnishdesignshop.com/decoration-candleholders-skultuna-the-factory-the-factory-candleholder-brass-p-11131.html" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/3fc463c44c90.jpg" width="350" height="350" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/94e6968ad4cf.jpg" width="415" height="279" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/e680f7a72fbb.jpg" width="415" height="277" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/d372753af0d8.jpg" width="350" height="350" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	HEXAGON HONEY by Maksim Arbuzov
</h3>
<p>
	俄罗斯的设计师 Maksim Arbuzov 认为，蜂蜜应该保持它本来的样子，于是用透明的六角形瓶子做蜂蜜的瓶身，让蜂蜜自然的颜色透出来。木质的盖子也是六角形的，盖子里直接连接了蜂蜜棒，很方便。为了让这些蜂蜜在货架上排列成蜂窝的样子，设计师在瓶子下面空出了放盖子的凹槽，能稳固的排成一面。<a href="http://www.maksimarbuzov.com/#/honey/" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/246e4008aa2d.jpg" width="730" height="487" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/7204ec1ee61a.jpg" width="730" height="487" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
